{"tid":2250122,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警紀律部隊宿舍附近荔景邨截查44歲男  檢10萬元毒品","createTime":"2020-10-20T01:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T02:07:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f6b233c7145d52d014cae1376d085ab8b67d1fea","tid":2250122,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:32:53.000Z","msg":"警方在葵涌荔景邨拘捕一名男子，檢獲約值10萬元的懷疑「冰」毒、懷疑氯胺酮及懷疑可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n葵青警區特別職務隊人員根據線報及經深入調查，昨晚上約7時，在葵涌荔景邨安景樓地下截查一名44歲姓翁本地男子，並在其身上檢獲約79克懷疑「冰」毒、約34克懷疑氯胺酮及約9.5克懷疑可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n行動中檢獲的毒品市值約10萬元。該名男子涉嫌「販毒」被捕，他現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，販毒屬嚴重罪行，根據香港法例第134章《危險藥物條例》，一經定罪，最高可判處罰款500萬港元及終身監禁，市民切勿以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline .com/news/realtime/hk/1901903</code></pre>"},{"pid":"85c87cc2880d3c64618038172d673bdd811b651c","tid":2250122,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:34:54.000Z","msg":"又食冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea0afc0d8bbe060d86200515d9c54546c3fc6e6","tid":2250122,"uid":18587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:35:57.000Z","msg":"可能係黑警或者家屬，平時好似會報疑犯職員，呢單無報"},{"pid":"242e82d9bca218d815a09e973c8082ac1f002f73","tid":2250122,"uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20191227-21_ssbgf_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20191227-21_ssbgf_1200x0.png&h=e763f51e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51269b9b076975b1fadaddaf1116bf6d1cb840e0","tid":2250122,"uid":93649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T01:46:28.000Z","msg":"荔景村又唔一定狗"},{"pid":"fd7c79db95901ed620e5d56dfa927935278b7dbc","tid":2250122,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020